Purpose: Strip model “personality” and flatten text into canonical form.
Ross‑OS applies three sequential rule groups:

A. Lexical Sanitization
Remove conversational padding

Strip Markdown, emojis, backticks

Normalize whitespace

Enforce UTF‑8 NFC

B. Entity & Intent Isolation
Extract imperative verb phrase → primary_action

Extract key‑value pairs → parameters.key_variables

C. Canonical Format String
All normalized text compiles into:

Code
[Action]. [Parameter 1]: [Value 1]. [Parameter 2]: [Value 2].
This becomes clean_text_content.
